#: ../../source/setup.rst:2
msgid "Model Setup"
msgstr "模型设置"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:5
msgid "Check Model"
msgstr "检查模型"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:7
msgid "Before you begin, make sure the armature model is properly prepared."
msgstr "在开始之前，请确保骨架模型已经正确准备。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:9
msgid ""
"Make sure the vertex weights are assigned correctly, especially for the "
"bones that will participate in the physics simulation. Incorrect or "
"overlapping weights are one of the most common causes of unexpected "
"simulation issues."
msgstr "请确保顶点权重分配正确，尤其是参与物理模拟的骨骼。错误或重叠的权重是导致模拟异常的最常见原因之一。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst
msgid ""
"While the following setup steps are not strictly required, starting with "
"these standards will help you avoid many common problems later:"
msgstr "虽然以下设置步骤并非强制要求，但按照这些规范开始可以避免后续出现许多常见问题："

#: ../../source/setup.rst:16
msgid "Place the model at the world origin ( 0, 0, 0 )."
msgstr "将模型放置在世界原点（0, 0, 0）。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:17
msgid ""
"This makes it easier to align with other assets and ensures consistency "
"when exporting."
msgstr "这样可以更方便地与其他资源对齐，并在导出时保持一致性。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:18
msgid "Face the -Y axis."
msgstr "面向 -Y 轴方向。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:19
msgid ""
"In Blender, by convention characters usually face the negative Y "
"direction. This aligns better with many add-ons, rigging tools, and "
"export pipelines (e.g. for game engines)."
msgstr "在 Blender 中，按照惯例角色通常面向负 Y 方向。这样可以更好地兼容许多插件、绑定工具以及导出流程（例如用于游戏引擎）。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:21
msgid "Apply all transforms (:menuselection:`Ctrl + A --> Apply All Transforms`)."
msgstr "应用所有变换（:menuselection:`Ctrl + A --> 应用全部变换`）。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:22
msgid ""
"Make sure location, rotation, and scale are all applied before rigging or"
" running simulations. Non-applied transforms can cause inconsistent bone "
"behavior, incorrect physics, or scaling issues when importing into other "
"software."
msgstr "在进行绑定或运行模拟之前，请确保位置（Location）、旋转（Rotation）和缩放（Scale）都已经应用。未应用的变换可能导致骨骼行为异常、物理结果错误，或者在导入其他软件时出现比例问题。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:33
msgid "Root Operations"
msgstr "Root 操作"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:35 ../../source/setup.rst:110
#: ../../source/setup.rst:131
msgid ""
"Visibility panel\n"
":align: center"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/setup.rst:40
msgid ""
"The purpose of **Root Operations** is to configure an Empty object as the"
" `Root Empty` for the current armature model. Through this root object, "
"all auxiliary elements used in physics simulation — such as rigid bodies,"
" joints, or temporary helper objects — can be organized under a single "
"parent."
msgstr ""
"**Root Operations** 的作用是为当前骨架模型设置一个空对象（Empty）作为 `Root Empty`。通过该 Root "
"对象，可以将物理模拟所需的所有辅助元素 —— 例如刚体（Rigid Bodies）、关节（Joints）或临时辅助对象 —— "
"统一组织在同一个父级之下。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:43
msgid ""
"This approach makes it much easier to manage multi-character scenes in a "
"clean and structured way. For example:"
msgstr "这种方式可以更清晰地管理多角色场景。例如："

#: ../../source/setup.rst:46
msgid ""
"`Linking` and `Library Overrides` become straightforward, since you only "
"need to link a single collection."
msgstr "`链接（Linking）` 和 `库覆写（Library Overrides）` 会变得更加简单，因为你只需要链接一个集合。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:47
msgid ""
"You can also attach custom-purpose objects to the root, such as special "
"effect emitters, or camera focus targets."
msgstr "你也可以将一些自定义用途的对象附加到 Root 上，例如特效发射器、摄像机对焦目标。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:49
msgid ""
"This add-on requires that every armature model be placed under a `Root "
"Empty`."
msgstr "该插件要求每个骨架模型都必须放置在一个 `Root Empty` 之下。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:52
msgid ""
"This requirement is fundamental to how the add-on organizes physics data."
" If this workflow does not fit your project, the add-on may not be "
"suitable for your pipeline."
msgstr "这是插件组织物理数据的核心结构。如果这种工作流程不适合你的项目，"
"那么该插件可能不适合你的制作流程。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:55
msgid "There are two possible scenarios:"
msgstr "通常有两种情况："

#: ../../source/setup.rst:57
msgid ""
"Your armature does not yet have an empty parent → use :ref:`create-root` "
"to generate one."
msgstr "骨架还没有 Empty 父级 → 使用 :ref:`create-root` 创建一个。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:58
msgid ""
"Your armature already has a direct empty parent → use :ref:`select-root` "
"to assign it as the root."
msgstr "骨架已经有一个直接的 Empty 父级 → 使用 :ref:`select-root` 将其指定为 Root。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:63
msgid "Create Root"
msgstr "创建 Root"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:65
msgid ""
"This operation creates a new Empty object as the parent of the selected "
"armature model, serving as its root."
msgstr "该操作会创建一个新的 Empty 对象，并将其设置为所选骨架模型的父级，作为 Root。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:72
msgid "You can set the Empty's `name`, `display type`, and `scale`."
msgstr "你可以设置 Empty 的 `名称 (Name)`、`显示类型 (Display Type)` 和 `缩放 (Scale)`。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:73
msgid ""
"The root will be created at the **current location of the armature** and "
"will automatically become its parent. (Therefore, we recommend placing "
"the armature at the world origin)"
msgstr "Root 会创建在 **骨架当前位置**，并自动成为其父对象。"
"（因此建议将骨架放置在世界原点）"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:75
msgid ""
"Once the root is created, the armature's **Transform** (`Location`, "
"`Rotation`, `Scale`) will be locked."
msgstr "创建 Root 后，骨架的 **Transform** （位置 Location、旋转 Rotation、缩放 Scale）将被锁定。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:76
msgid ""
"Finally, the armature will be set to **Show In Front** , which helps keep"
" it visible over other objects."
msgstr "最后，骨架会被设置为 **Show In Front（始终显示在前）**，"
"以便在其他物体前方保持可见。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:81
msgid "Select Root"
msgstr "选择 Root"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:83
msgid ""
"This operation allows you to select an existing **direct parent** of the "
"selected armature as its root."
msgstr "该操作允许你将所选骨架的现有 **直接父级对象** 指定为 Root。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:90
msgid "Currently, only Empty objects that are direct parents are supported."
msgstr "目前仅支持作为 **直接父级** 的空对象（Empty）。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:91
msgid ""
"Although the Empty does not have to coincide with the armature's origin, "
"it is recommended to align them for cleaner transformations."
msgstr "虽然 Empty 不一定必须与骨架原点重合，但建议将它们对齐，以获得更清晰的变换结构。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:92
msgid ""
"Once the root is selected, the armature's **Transform** (`Location`, "
"`Rotation`, `Scale`) will be locked."
msgstr "选择 Root 后，骨架的 **Transform** （位置 Location、旋转 Rotation、缩放 Scale）将被锁定。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:93
msgid ""
"Finally, the armature will be set to **Show In Front**, which helps keep "
"it visible over other objects."
msgstr "最后，骨架会被设置为 **Show In Front（始终显示在前）**，"
"以便在其他物体前方保持可见。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:96
msgid "Clear"
msgstr "清理"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:98
msgid ""
"This operation removes all rigid bodies and constraints under the "
"`rigidbodies`, `joints`, and `temporary` groups. It will also unlock the "
"armature's **Transform** (`Location`, `Rotation`, `Scale`). After "
"performing a :menuselection:`Clear` operation, you may also choose to "
"delete the `Root Empty` object if it is no longer needed."
msgstr "该操作会移除 `rigidbodies`、`joints` 和 `temporary` 组下的所有刚体与约束。"
"同时也会解除骨架 **Transform** （位置 Location、旋转 Rotation、缩放 Scale）的锁定。"
"执行 :menuselection:`Clear` 操作后，如果不再需要 `Root Empty`，"
"你也可以选择将其删除。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst
msgid ""
"Clearing everything will remove all physics-related data. Once deleted, "
"the model will no longer participate in physics simulation unless the "
"setup is rebuilt."
msgstr "执行清理操作会移除所有与物理相关的数据。"
"删除后，模型将不再参与物理模拟，除非重新构建物理系统。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:106
msgid "Visibility"
msgstr "可见性"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:108
msgid ""
"You can use the buttons under the **Visibility** section to show or hide "
"related objects in the scene:"
msgstr "你可以使用 **Visibility** 区域中的按钮来显示或隐藏场景中的相关对象："

#: ../../source/setup.rst:115
msgid ":menuselection:`Mesh` — Show or hide the model meshes."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Mesh` — 显示或隐藏模型网格。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:116
msgid ":menuselection:`Armature` — Show or hide the armature."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Armature` — 显示或隐藏骨架。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:117
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Rigid Body` — Show or hide all rigid body objects used "
"for simulation."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Rigid Body` — 显示或隐藏所有用于模拟的刚体对象。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:118
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Rigid Body Name` — Toggle the display of rigid body names"
" in the viewport. which helps in identifying and debugging complex "
"setups."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Rigid Body Name` — 在视口中显示或隐藏刚体名称，"
"有助于识别和调试复杂的设置。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:120
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Joint` — Show or hide the joints (Rigid Body Constraints)"
" that connect Rigid Bodies."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Joint` — 显示或隐藏连接刚体的关节（Rigid Body Constraints）。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:121
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Joint Name` — Display or hide the joint names in the "
"viewport for easier inspection."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Joint Name` — 在视口中显示或隐藏关节名称，以便更容易检查。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:122
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Temporary Objects` — Show or hide helper or temporary "
"objects generated during setup."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Temporary Objects` — 显示或隐藏设置过程中生成的辅助或临时对象。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:123
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Reset` — Restore all visibility options to their default "
"state."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Reset` — 将所有可见性选项恢复为默认状态。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:126
msgid "Build Rig Physics"
msgstr "构建 Rig 物理"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:128
msgid ""
"After adding all :ref:`Rigid Bodies <rigid_body>` and :ref:`Joints "
"<joint>`, click the :menuselection:`Build Rig Physics` button to generate"
" the physical simulation system."
msgstr "在添加完所有 :ref:`刚体 <rigid_body>` 和 :ref:`关节 <joint>` 之后，"
"点击 :menuselection:`Build Rig Physics` 按钮以生成物理模拟系统。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:136
msgid "During this process, the add-on will:"
msgstr "在此过程中，插件将会："

#: ../../source/setup.rst:138
msgid ""
"Temporarily mute **Parent constraints** and **IK constraints** to prevent"
" conflicts with the physics solver."
msgstr "临时禁用 **Parent 约束** 和 **IK 约束**，以避免与物理解算器发生冲突。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:139
msgid ""
"Identify rigid bodies without parent bones, and establish *fake parent "
"relationships* based on their connected joints."
msgstr "识别没有父骨骼的刚体，并根据其连接的关节建立 *虚拟父级关系（fake parent relationships）*。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:140
msgid ""
"Rebuild the rigid body hierarchy and update their transforms to align "
"with the armature's current pose."
msgstr "重建刚体层级结构，并更新其 Transform，使其与当前骨架姿态保持一致。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:141
msgid ""
"Automatically create non-collision constraints **(NCC)** between nearby "
"rigid bodies that should not collide, improving stability and avoiding "
"unwanted intersections."
msgstr "在不应发生碰撞的相邻刚体之间自动创建非碰撞约束 **(NCC)**，"
"以提高稳定性并避免不必要的相互穿插。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:143
msgid ""
"For dynamic bones, attach hidden Empty objects as tracking targets "
"(`bone_physics_rigid_track`) to allow bones to be driven by Rigid Bodies "
"through ``COPY_TRANSFORMS`` or ``COPY_ROTATION`` constraints."
msgstr ""
"对于动态骨骼，会附加隐藏的 Empty 对象作为跟踪目标（`bone_physics_rigid_track`），"
"从而通过 ``COPY_TRANSFORMS`` 或 ``COPY_ROTATION`` 约束使骨骼能够被刚体驱动。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:145
msgid ""
"Restore and synchronize all constraint states once the system is fully "
"initialized."
msgstr ""
"在系统完全初始化后恢复并同步所有约束状态。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:147
msgid ""
"When the build is complete, the :menuselection:`Clean Rig Physics` button"
" will appear — clicking it will remove the constructed simulation system "
"and restore the rig to its pre-build state."
msgstr ""
"构建完成后，会出现 :menuselection:`Clean Rig Physics` 按钮。"
"点击该按钮可以移除已构建的模拟系统，并将 Rig 恢复到构建之前的状态。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:151
msgid ""
"Always **save your project** before performing any physics build or "
"cleanup operations."
msgstr ""
"在执行任何物理构建或清理操作之前，请务必 **保存你的项目**。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:154
msgid ""
"If you are using a *single-file workflow*, pay close attention to the "
"operation order. After :menuselection:`Build Rig Physics` is complete, "
"you may preview the simulation by playing the timeline. When finished, "
"follow this exact sequence before cleaning:"
msgstr ""
"如果你使用的是 *单文件工作流程*，请特别注意操作顺序。"
"在 :menuselection:`Build Rig Physics` 完成后，可以通过播放时间轴预览模拟。"
"预览完毕，在清理之前请严格按照以下步骤操作："

#: ../../source/setup.rst:158
msgid "Pause the timeline playback."
msgstr "暂停时间轴播放。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:159
msgid "Press :kbd:`Shift` + :kbd:`←` to reset the timeline to the first frame."
msgstr "按 :kbd:`Shift` + :kbd:`←` 将时间轴重置到第一帧。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:160
msgid "Click :menuselection:`Clean Rig Physics`."
msgstr "点击 :menuselection:`Clean Rig Physics`。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:162
msgid ""
"Failing to reset the timeline before cleaning may cause **Blender to "
"crash**. This happens because the physics system is still actively "
"simulating while the rig hierarchy and constraints are being removed, "
"leading to dependency conflicts."
msgstr ""
"如果在清理之前没有重置时间轴，可能会导致 **Blender 崩溃**。"
"这是因为在移除 Rig 层级结构和约束时，物理系统仍在运行模拟，"
"从而引发依赖关系冲突。"

#: ../../source/setup.rst:166
msgid ""
"In *multi-file collaborative workflows*, animators can safely disable "
"physics temporarily by performing :menuselection:`Clean Rig Physics` "
"before animation editing, and rebuild it again when needed."
msgstr ""
"在 *多文件协作工作流程* 中，动画师可以在编辑动画之前执行 "
":menuselection:`Clean Rig Physics` 来临时禁用物理系统，"
"并在需要时重新构建。"

